# Environment variables for devvit-ski
#
# Copy this file to .env and fill in any values you need.
# The dev script (npm run dev:devvit) loads .env via dotenv-cli before
# starting devvit playtest, so future env vars can be added here.
#
# Currently no environment variables are required — this file exists
# as a placeholder so contributors know .env is intentionally gitignored
# and not missing by accident.
